URL: http://www.feelgoodworld.org/

FeelGood World is a program that transforms students into successful social entrepreneurs and responsible global citizens – a.k.a. “changemakers.”

==Offline==
FeelGood is turning college students into world-changing social entrepreneurs by running on-campus Grilled Cheese Delis...yum.

And here’s what’s really cool: All the money they earn is invested in organizations working for the sustainable end of hunger!

But that’s just the beginning. They’re also learning about sustainable models of development, and what it means to be a global citizen.

==Online==
This is where those same students (and pretty much anyone else) engage in mind-shifting explorations—what we call Changemaker Journeys —and then take creative, hunger-solving actions—what we call Changemaker Challenges.

And to sweeten the deal, all Changemaker Challenges earn Cheese Points: FeelGood’s convertible currency that can be invested in FeelGood students, as well as products that generate yet more investment dollars of the sustainable end of hunger.

